title: Getting Started
text:
First, it will be helpful to access the full code repository for this workshop. There are a couple ways to do this.

Fork the repository on GitHub: Go to the GitHub page for this repository: https://github.com/swforrest/ESA2025_animal_movement_workshop
Download the repository as a ZIP file: You can do this by clicking on the green “Code” button at the top right of the GitHub page and selecting “Download ZIP”. Once downloaded, unzip the file to a location on your computer where you can easily find it.

title: ESA2025_animal_movement_workshop
text:

To get started with the materials for this workshop, please visit the Getting Started page.
